### System06 CVE-2025-0092	A-289375038
@code
android-12.0.0_r1/platform/packages/apps/Bluetooth/0002-Reset-permissions-for-not-bonded-device.bulletin.patch
patch -p1 < 0002-Reset-permissions-for-not-bonded-device.bulletin.patch
